title: 2002–03 Moldovan Cup
text:
2002–03 <a href="Moldovan%20Cup">Moldovan Cup</a> was the twelfth edition of the <a href="Moldova">Moldova</a>n annual <a href="Association%20football">football</a> tournament.
Round of 16.
The first legs were played on September 4, 2002. The second legs were played on October 16, 2002.
Quarterfinals.
The first legs were played on October 30, 2002. The second legs were played on November 13, 2002.
Semifinals.
The first legs were played on March 19, 2003. The second legs were played on April 10, 2003.
